== Before committing any changes ==

Ensure that the Perl tests run through without any problems.

== Running the Perl tests ==
 * If necessary, put symlinks in the project's root directory to the executables you want to test.
 * Ensure that . is included in your PATH, so that the Perl tests find your binaries.
 * Use `prove -l -v t` so that the output of tests is verbose (and hence includes TODO messages.
